FBIS4-60700 "drnes103_g_94003" FBIS-NES-94-103 Daily Report 26 May 1994 Sudan Foreign Ministry Condemns Divisions Within OAU Foreign Ministry Condemns Divisions Within OAU EA2605195594 Khartoum SUNA in Arabic 1500 GMT 26 May 94 EA2605195594 Khartoum SUNA Arabic BFN [Text] Khartoum, 26 May (SUNA) -- Sudan has expressed its condemnation of all attempts at division and fragmentation and the lies of the advocates of the right to self-determination for illusory racial entities. The Foreign Ministry said in a statement issued yesterday to mark the 31st anniversary of the OAU's establishment, that the anniversary comes at a time when the continent is becoming marginalized as part of the so-called new world order. It called for more solidarity, vigilance, and unity in the face of the conspiracies being hatched against the African continent.
